*Rider Payments Receipts*











In the rapidly changing world of logistics, cash handling and
reconciliation must be a seamless part of everyday cash flow. Currently,
the absence of receipts for online transfers creates information gaps
regarding transfers made by riders in the past.


To address this, we are introducing* Rider payment receipt *- an upgrade to
our workflow, specifically designed to bring transparency and precision to
every transaction done by rider.


What=E2=80=99s New?




   -

   *Digital Receipts:* Riders can now see and verify payments made to a
   certain account in the Rider App during the time of transfer.


   -

   *View Proof in BOP:* Managers gain instant access to transaction
   receipts on the web dashboard

   -

   *Assessment Logs:* Every online payment now carries a verifiable digital
   footprint, including timestamps and payment references, visible to every=
one
   with access.



