   -

   *Information Accuracy: *Ensuring 100% information accuracy for every
   transaction will ensure the rider is always aware of the transfer made w=
ith
   actual deposit details.

   -

   *Workflow Clarity: *Provides store managers with the documentation
   needed to confirm payments instantly, reducing back-and-forth communicat=
ion
   with the riders.


   -

   *Financial Accuracy:* This strengthens financial controls and ensures
   that all digital transfers are fully accounted for within the system.

